coordinates%20for%20where%20the%20pots%20have%20come%20to%20rest%20on%20the%20ocean%20floor.%20Then%2C%20they%20head%20back%20to%20land%20and%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20after%2012%20to%2024%20hours%2C%20but%20in%20some%20cases%20up%20to%20a%20week%2C%20fishers%20return%20to%20the%20same%20coordinates%2C%20pull%20in%20their%20pots%2C%20and%20examine%20their%20catches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20real%20work%20begins.%20Every%20jurisdiction%20has%20rules%20dictating%20the%20size%20and%20weight%20of%20crabs%20that%20fishers%20can%20harvest%2C%20so%20crabbers%20must%20measure%20each%20crustacean's%20weight%20and%20shell%20size%20and%20then%20count%2C%20grade%2C%20and%20sort%20their%20hauls%2C%20as%20well%20as%20record%20the%20data%20they've%20collected%2C%20before%20they%20can%20consider%20the%20catch%20a%20job%20officially%20done.%20Until%20recently%2C%20most%20of%20these%20records%20have%20been%20written%20by%20hand%20in%20physical%20logbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManaging%20these%20tasks%20and%20meeting%20rising%20consumer%20demands%20for%20sustainable%20crab%20meat%20isn't%20easy.%20But%20a%20startup%20in%20Palo%20Alto%2C%20California%2C%20called%20SeafoodAI%2C%20says%20it%20has%20an%20AI-powered%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20SeafoodAI%20released%20CrabScan360%2C%20its%20tool%20designed%20to%20automate%20crab%20measurement%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20data%20recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Terry%2C%20SeafoodAI's%20founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20CrabScan360%20acts%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btireless%20deckhand%26quot%3B%20who%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkraft-heinz-ai-lighthouse-helps-forecast-supply-chain-demands-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-powered%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20collect%20all%20necessary%20data%2C%20including%20every%20crab's%20size%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20grade.%20The%20software%20also%20uses%20this%20data%20to%20determine%20which%20crabs%20can%20remain%20part%20of%20any%20given%20haul%20and%20which%20ones%20fishers%20must%20toss%20back%20into%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e4e85b5-06c5-4a8b-919a-a0debe3f9f46%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20AI%20is%20helping%20crab%20fishers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrabScan360%20comes%20in%20two%20versions%3A%20one%20for%20the%20field%20and%20one%20for%20the%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portable%20field%20version%2C%20released%20in%20April%2C%20is%20about%20the%20size%20of%20a%20carry-on%20suitcase%20and%20was%20built%20to%20deploy%20quickly%20on%20boats%20and%20docks.%20Fishers%20put%20one%20crab%20at%20a%20time%20on%20the%20scanner%2C%20and%20the%20device%20snaps%20photos.%20It%20uses%20sensors%20and%20built-in%20custom%20software%20to%20instantly%20analyze%20and%20log%20each%20crab's%20size%2C%20weight%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20legal%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20factory%20version%2C%20which%20is%20in%20development%2C%20is%20fully%20automated.%20Crabs%20move%20along%20a%20conveyor%20belt%20and%20pass%20under%20a%20scanner%20that%20evaluates%20each%20one.%20Crabs%20are%20then%20sorted%20based%20on%20the%20analysis.%20Each%20scan%20creates%20an%20individual%20data%20record%20that's%20uploaded%20to%20the%20cloud.%20Users%20can%20then%20log%20in%20and%20see%20trends%20such%20as%20average%20size%2C%20yield%2C%20and%20legal%20catch%20percentages%20across%20an%20entire%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrabScan360%20also%20creates%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-trucking-logistics-uber-freight-tech-optimize-routes-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20fingerprint%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20every%20scanned%20crab%2C%20providing%20%26quot%3Binstant%2C%20accurate%20digital%20records%20tied%20to%20the%20specific%20harvest%20location%2C%20time%2C%20and%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20Terry%20said.%20This%20data%20travels%20with%20each%20crab%20as%20it%20moves%20through%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20creating%20a%20clear%20chai