%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20help%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20give%20my%20money%20back%20to%20society%20much%20faster%20than%20I%20had%20originally%20planned.%20I%20will%20give%20away%20virtually%20all%20my%20wealth%20through%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%20over%20the%20next%2020%20years%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20saving%20and%20improving%20lives%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Microsoft%20cofounder%20initially%20made%20the%20announcement%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20to%20mark%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20which%20is%20the%20third-largest%20charitable%20foundation%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20charitable%20foundation%20was%20launched%20in%202000%20by%20Bill%20Gates%20and%20his%20then-wife%2C%20Melinda%20Gates%2C%20when%20they%20were%2044%20and%2035%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20said%20in%20the%20interview%20that%20the%20foundation%20had%20%26quot%3Bachieved%20far%20more%20than%20I%20%E2%80%94%20or%20I%20think%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20expected%26quot%3B%20and%20helped%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20childhood%20deaths%20from%2010%20million%20to%205%20million%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20he%20was%20announcing%20plans%20to%20sunset%20the%20operation%2C%20he%20said%20it%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20difference%26quot%3B%20to%20spend%20its%20resources%20%26quot%3Bnow%20versus%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20trying%20to%20steward%20our%20money%20for%20some%20weird%20legacy%20thing.%20If%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20forever%20foundation%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20able%20to%20spend%20%249%20billion%20a%20year%2C%20we'd%20have%20to%20drop%20down%20to%20spending%20like%20%246%20billion%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNormally%20we're%20saving%20lives%20for%20%242%2C000%20or%20%243%2C000.%20But%20given%20the%20problems%20that%20are%20out%20there%2C%20we're%20actually%20now%20saving%20lives%20for%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20a%20miraculous%20time.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20hundred%20billion%20we've%20spent%20is%20to%20build%20a%20pipeline%2C%20and%20the%20most%20important%20stuff%20the%20foundation%20is%20doing%20is%20the%20stuff%20that's%20in%20the%20R%26amp%3BD%20pipeline%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stepped%20down%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-pay-compensation-cybersecurity-ai-tech-stock-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMicrosoft's%20CEO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202008%20to%20devote%20more%20time%20to%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20held%20%2469%20billion%20in%20assets%20as%20of%202020%20and%20had%20an%20endowment%20of%20%2475.2%20billion%20as%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20donated%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20charitable%20causes%2C%20including%20global%20health%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20and%20water%20sanitation%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-career-lessons-berkshire-hathaway-succession-stocks-value-investing-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-ceo-resignation-investing-succession-greg-abel-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheadlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20when%20he%20announced%20he%20was%20stepping%20down%20from%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20was%20central%20to%20the%20Gates%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20served%20as%20a%20trustee%20of%20the%20foundation%20from%202006%20to%202022%2C%20and%